st:\n</p>\n<pre>\ns88&#160;:= 16*rankIndex(s) + fileIndex(s);\ns88&#160;:= 16*(rankIndex(b) + fileIndex(b) - fileIndex(a)) + fileIndex(a);\ns88&#160;:= 16*rankIndex(b) + 16*fileIndex(b) - 15*fileIndex(a);\nif ( s88 &amp; 0x88)\n   intersection off board;\nelse\n   sq&#160;:= ((sq88 &gt;&gt; 1) &amp; 56) + (sq88 &amp; 7);\n</pre>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"C-Source_4\">C-Source</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Intersection_Squares&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: C-Source\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<pre>\n/****************************************\n * return: intersection square (if any)\n *          of file of square a\n *          with anti-diagonal of square b\n *         -1 if no intersection exists\n ****************************************/\nint intersectFileAnt(int a, int b) {\n   int s88 = 2*(b &amp; 56) + 16*(b &amp; 7) - 15*(a &amp; 7);\n   return (((s88 &gt;&gt; 1) &amp; 56) + (s88 &amp; 7)) | ( -(s88 &amp; 0x88) &gt;&gt; 31);\n}\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Diagonal_and_Anti-Diagonal\">Diagonal and Anti-Diagonal</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Intersection_Squares&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15\" title=\"Edit section: Diagonal and Anti-Diagonal\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>or vice versa Anti-Diagonal and Diagonal\n</p>\n<pre>\n. . . . . . . .\n. . . . . . . /\n\\ . . . . . / .\n. b . . . / . .\n. . \\ . / . . .\n. . . s . . . .\n. . a . \\ . . .\n. / . . . \\ . .\n</pre>\n<p>with\n</p>\n<pre>diagonalIndex&#160;:= rankIndex - fileIndex;\n</pre>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n\n<tr>\n<th> r/f\n</th>\n<th> 0\n</th>\n<th> 1\n</th>\n<th> 2\n</th>\n<th> 3\n</th>\n<th> 4\n</th>\n<th> 5\n</th>\n<th> 6\n</th>\n<th> 7\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th> 7\n</th>\n<td style=\"text-align:ri